{"tid":1335183,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"經濟日報副社長石鏡泉鼓吹虐待兒童，請市民表達關注！","createTime":"2019-07-20T11:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T18:54:01.000Z","uid":276716,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"61c680bf9e62ff0a0043cb50d0efc971d0da1d34","tid":1335183,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:44:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRY7to5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRY7to5.jpg&h=be301304&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n《香港經濟日報》副社長石鏡泉在守護香港集會上，批評年輕人的暴力衝擊行爲，指他們受美國惡勢力煽惑，又高呼「多謝美國協助中國崛起」。他又指，並非所有市民皆是「暴徒」，惟「一粒老鼠屎打砸一鍋粥」，示威者砸磚、砸鐵枝的行爲實在不能原諒，又揚言「教仔」應要用藤條及塑膠水喉通，促請他們停止「亂中亂港」。"},{"pid":"b9b6192c83f3741419911be041e63807aef9eea6","tid":1335183,"uid":276716,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:46:17.000Z","msg":"如知名人士或報社社長的言論涉嫌鼓吹虐兒，請向保護兒童組織表達關注。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.aca.org.hk/top-cpci.htm#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aca.org.hk%2Ftop-cpci.htm%23&d=5riwYeXkLlljSywqzybc4s%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=298cbb29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.aca.org.hk/top-cpci.htm#</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.unicef.org.hk/leadership/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unicef.org.hk%2Fleadership%2F&d=5riwYeXkLlljSywqzybc4s%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=32a16f2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.unicef.org.hk/leadership/</a>"},{"pid":"69e4830b73db093d12604fed770b0d8a7a295487","tid":1335183,"uid":11804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:46:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ddd51911fb386d260f00a7a5756a514c4c81c112","tid":1335183,"uid":275370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:47:27.000Z","msg":"豬隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e86cbc5fea82a00d4fd517dec7628e56776f132","tid":1335183,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r